//To download chrome driver
1. first check version of your pc chrome browser
2. download particular version driver

//How to check version of your pc chrome browser
a. At the top right corner of your chrome browser, your will see (:) three dot sign
b. click on (:) --> Help --> About Google Chrome

//How to download chrome driver of particular version
a. open any browser, type "chrome driver download" and enter
b. search chrome driver of particular version, select driver for windows 64 and copy the link and paste in browser url
c. download the driver
d. place the driver in D drive and connect it with project below way

  System.setProperty("webdriver.gecko.driver", "D:\\alldriver\\geckodriver-v0.33.0-win32\\geckodriver.exe");
	WebDriver driver = new FirefoxDriver();
